Module ZiqiYang

Package org.ziqi.gameEngine

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    GameEngine
    GameEngine singleton class to take charge of all sectors of the running game by dispatching jobs to its attached managers and screen player.
    GameObjectFactory
    GameObjectFactory class takes charge of generating specific GameObject by given type and position.
    GraphicUnitRenderer
    GraphicUnitRenderer class takes charge of rendering graphic units of specific GameObjects on gaming screen.
    Logger
    Logger class takes charge of logging different levels of console message for each GameManager.
